<li><i>The Charlatan</i> (1974)</li>
<li><i>O Babylon!</i> (1976)</li>
<li><i>Remembrance</i> (1977)</li>
<li><i>Pantomime</i> (1978)</li>
<li><i>The Isle Is Full of Noises</i> (1982)</li>
<li><i>The Haitian Earth</i> (1984)</li>
<li><i>Three Plays: The Last Carnival, Beef, No Chicken, and A Branch of the Blue Nile</i> (1986)</li>
<li><i>Steel</i> (1991)</li>
<li><i>Odyssey: a Stage Version</i> (1993)</li>
<li><i>The Capeman</i> (1997), (livret), comédie musicale de <a href="/wiki/Paul_Simon_(chanteur)" title="Paul Simon (chanteur)">Paul Simon</a> dont a été tiré le CD <i><a href="/wiki/Songs_from_The_Capeman" title="Songs from The Capeman">Songs from The Capeman</a></i>.</li>
<li><i>Walker and The Ghost Dance</i> (2002)</li>
<li><i>Moon-Child</i> (2011)</li>
<li><i>O Starry Starry Night</i> (2014)</li></ul>
</div>
